@*
    /docs/features — field reference for the major Modern COMPASS features.
    Field descriptions are derived from the Modern view models in
    Models/Modern/ and the EF Core models in Models/. Where a value is
    constrained to a vocabulary the allowed values are listed in the "Notes"
    column.
*@

<div class="developers-docs__intro govuk-!-margin-bottom-6">
    <span class="govuk-caption-xl">Reference</span>
    <h1 class="govuk-heading-xl govuk-!-margin-bottom-2">Feature reference</h1>
    <p class="govuk-body-l govuk-!-margin-bottom-0">
        Field-level reference for each Modern feature surface. Pair this with
        <a class="govuk-link" href="@Url.Action("DataModels", "Docs")">Data models</a>
        when authoring reports, integrations, or new UI components.
    </p>
</div>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-l" id="overview">Overview</h2>
<p class="govuk-body">Conventions used in the tables below:</p>
<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
    <li><strong>Modern field</strong> &mdash; the property name on the Modern view model (for example <code>WorkItem.RagStatusId</code>).</li>
    <li><strong>DB column</strong> &mdash; the EF Core entity property that backs it (for example <code>Project.RagStatusLookupId</code>).</li>
    <li><strong>Type</strong> &mdash; the C# / SQL type. <code>string(n)</code> means <code>nvarchar(n)</code>.</li>
    <li><strong>Required</strong> &mdash; yes if the column is non-nullable at the database level.</li>
    <li><strong>Notes</strong> &mdash; allowed values, units, foreign keys, Modern view link.</li>
</ul>

<div class="govuk-inset-text">
    If this page disagrees with a model class in <code>Models/</code> or
    <code>Models/Modern/</code>, the model class is correct. Open a PR to fix
    the docs.
</div>

<hr class="govuk-section-break govuk-section-break--l govuk-section-break--visible">

<div class="developers-feature-reference">

<h2 class="govuk-heading-l" id="work-items">Work items</h2>
<p class="govuk-body">
    Modern view model <code>Compass.Models.Modern.Work.WorkItem</code> wraps
    EF entity <code>Compass.Models.Project</code>. List view at
    <code>/modern/work</code>; detail at <code>/modern/work/{id}</code>.
</p>
<table class="govuk-table">
    <thead class="govuk-table__head">
        <tr class="govuk-table__row">
            <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Modern field</th>
            <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">DB column</th>
            <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Type</th>
            <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Notes</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody class="govuk-table__body">
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Id</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Project.Id</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell">int (identity)</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Primary key. URL: <code>/modern/work/{Id}</code>.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Title</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Project.Title</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell">string(200), required</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Display title.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Aim</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Project.Aim</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell">string(4000)</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">One-paragraph &ldquo;why&rdquo;.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Description</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Project.StrategicObjectives</code> (legacy fallback)</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">string (max)</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Long-form description shown on detail.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ProblemStatement</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ProjectProblemStatement.Statement</code> (latest)</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">string (max)</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Versioned via <code>ProjectProblemStatementHistory</code>.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Status</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Project.Status</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell">string(50), required</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">One of <code>Active</code>, <code>Paused</code>, <code>Completed</code>, <code>Cancelled</code>. Drives the Modern register tabs.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>RagStatusId</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Project.RagStatusLookupId</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell">int? (FK <code>RagStatusLookup</code>)</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Current RAG. Surfaced as a badge via <code>_WorkRagBadge</code>.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>PriorityId</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Project.DeliveryPriorityId</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell">int? (FK <code>DeliveryPriority</code>)</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">P1..P4 priority lookup.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>PriorityChangeReason</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Project.DeliveryPriorityChangeReason</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell">string(2000)</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Justification on priority change.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>DeliveryPhaseId</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Project.PhaseId</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell">int? (FK <code>PhaseLookup</code>)</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Discovery / Alpha / Beta / Live / Retired.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>WorkTypeId</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Project.BusinessAreaId</code> (legacy) or work-type lookup</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">int?</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Categorisation for the Modern register.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>PortfolioId</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Project.PrimaryOrganizationalGroupId</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell">int? (FK <code>OrganizationalGroup</code>)</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Owning portfolio / group.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>PrimaryContactUserId</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Project.PrimaryContactUserId</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell">int? (FK <code>User</code>)</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Primary point of contact. Edited at <code>/modern/work/{id}/contact/primary</code>.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>BudgetOwnerUserId</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ProjectBudgetOwner.UserId</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell">int? (FK <code>User</code>)</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Edited at <code>/modern/work/{id}/contact/budget-owner</code>.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ActivityTypeId</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Project.ActivityTypeId</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell">int? (FK <code>ActivityTypeLookup</code>)</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Activity classification.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>RiskAppetiteId</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Project.RiskAppetiteId</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell">int? (FK <code>RiskAppetiteLookup</code>)</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Tolerance level.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>SubjectToSpendControl</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Project.SubjectToSpendControl</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell">bool</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">CDDO spend controls flag.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>FlagshipProject</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Project.IsFlagship</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell">bool</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Highlighted in registers and dashboards.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>IsCentralRiskBucket</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Project.IsCentralRiskBucket</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell">bool</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Holds central / cross-cutting risks rather than delivery.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>StartDate</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Project.StartDate</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell">datetime?</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">UTC.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>TargetEndDate</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Project.TargetDeliveryDate</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell">datetime?</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">UTC.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>MissionPillarId</code> + <code>MissionPillars</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ProjectMission</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell">int? + many-to-many</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Edited at <code>/modern/work/{id}/edit/strategic-alignment</code>.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>PriorityOutcomeId</code> + <code>PriorityOutcomes</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ProjectObjective</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell">int? + many-to-many</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Edited at <code>/modern/work/{id}/edit/strategic-alignment</code>.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Tags</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ProjectWorkItemTag</code> &harr; <code>WorkItemTagLookup</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell">collection</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Edited at <code>/modern/work/{id}/edit/tags</code>.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Directorates</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ProjectDirectorate</code> &harr; <code>Division</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell">collection</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Edited at <code>/modern/work/{id}/directorates</code>.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>GovernmentDepartments</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>ProjectGovernmentDepartment</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell">collection</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Edited at <code>/modern/work/{id}/edit/multi-dept</code>.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>CreatedAt</code> / <code>UpdatedAt</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Project.CreatedAt</code> / <code>UpdatedAt</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell">datetime</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">UTC. Maintained by EF.</td></tr>
        <tr class="govuk-table__row"><td class="govuk-table__cell">&mdash;</td><td class="govuk-table__cell"><code>Project.IsDeleted</code></td><td class="govuk-table__cell">bool</td><td class="govuk-table__cell">Soft-delete flag. The Modern register and JSON API always filter this.</td></tr>
    </tbody>
</table>

